# Kidney Breathalyzer Rules

## Medical Language
- Use "คัดกรองความเสี่ยง" — NEVER "วินิจฉัยโรค"
- Show disclaimer on every page with risk results
- AI gives general health info only, not diagnosis

## UI
- No Emoji — use Lucide icons only
- Thai UI text — follow Docs/UI_UX_SPECIFICATION.md
- Colors: accent #2B7FD4, surface #F5F5F7, Apple Health style

## Build Order
- P0 first: Landing → Dashboard → Measurement → Result
- Demo Mode must work without hardware
- Rule-based scoring only — no ML in MVP

## Code
- Logic in lib/, thin pages, feature components in components/
- Read AGENTS.md and Docs/ before implementing
